3.3 Example Scenario

Scenario: A DevOps engineer updates the payments Helm chart

Flow:
Engineer commits -> GitHub webhook triggers InfoGrid sync
      ↓
Parser detects new Helm values
      ↓
Knowledge graph updated: service, dependencies, environment
      ↓
AI layer updates recommendations for rollback/deploy
      ↓
CI/CD trigger suggestions updated


Result: Clients always see actionable, current intelligence, not outdated command
